; Description ...:
; Syntax ........: StartClockTowerBoost($bSwitchToBB = False, $bSwitchToNV = False)
; Parameters ....: $bSwitchToBB: Switch from Normal Village to Builder Base - $bSwitchToNV: Switch back to normal Village after Function ran
; Return values .: None
